CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Full House - Every seat in room was filled as Mr Jones' election took place. Councilman Dinan is standing in the foreground."
TitMainTitle: Councilman Charles Dinan standing at desk, with audience of men and women gathered in Pittsburgh City Council Chamber with flowers in foreground at City County Building
